		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Perestroika</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<div class="dablink">This article is about the term.  For the computer game, see <a href="/wiki/Perestroika_(computer_game)" title="Perestroika (computer game)" class="mw-redirect">Perestroika (computer game)</a>. For the play by Tony Kushner, see <a href="/wiki/Angels_in_America" title="Angels in America" class="mw-redirect">Angels in America</a>. For the movement in political science, see <a href="/wiki/Perestroika_Movement_(political_science)" title="Perestroika Movement (political science)">Perestroika Movement (political science)</a>.</div>
